article_title: The Week in Pictures: Bossypants Edition
article_text:
“Arise and take our stand for freedom as in the olden time.” Winston Churchill

“Proclaim Liberty throughout All the land unto All the Inhabitants Thereof.” Inscription on the Liberty Bell

og.description: So we’re supposed to ban “bossy” from our vocabulary, eh?  This, coming from the same folks who imposed the mandate that we all buy health insurance from government-run exchanges,…
